{"id": 1569, "genre": 1001, "title": "你觉得哪些话其实根本是另外一个意思？", "description": "一些不能从字面理解的高级汉语，我的情商已欠费！（题图来自：Rachel Denti）", "record_count": 6431, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170315160644QvbUaWk3ORyfq0B1.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-03-17T03:00:53Z", "options": [{"id": 179968, "content": "你去做好了", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973147}, {"id": 180480, "content": "\"早点睡我去洗澡了\" 意思是我不想聊了拜拜", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 463022}, {"id": 179969, "content": "马上＝‘什么马？’", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 958622}, {"id": 180225, "content": "哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973612}, {"id": 180481, "content": "有句话，不知当讲不当讲", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038691}, {"id": 179970, "content": "哦。看语境。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970605}, {"id": 180226, "content": "哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973612}, {"id": 180482, "content": "有句话，不知当讲不当讲", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1038691}, {"id": 179971, "content": "晚安就是不跟你聊了，我要做别的事了。", "image": null, "praise_count": 94, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973154}, {"id": 180227, "content": "你可真是个人才呀", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973620}, {"id": 183555, "content": "再说，再说", "image": "img/option/option/20170325074436B8qsJgPUuy0TcLrw", "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981753}, {"id": 179972, "content": "还好", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973156}, {"id": 182020, "content": "哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 977762}, {"id": 183556, "content": "也行吧", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981753}, {"id": 195332, "content": "不是我说你……", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011062}, {"id": 180485, "content": "讲真：", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 741711}, {"id": 180997, "content": "我尽力了，意思就是这是没你想的那么容易。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 113406}, {"id": 186373, "content": "你去吃饭吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 989624}, {"id": 186629, "content": "这题讲完就下课\n", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 990399}, {"id": 179974, "content": "历害死你", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 828370}, {"id": 180230, "content": "“就说两句话”", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973402}, {"id": 180486, "content": "我干了你随意", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974339}, {"id": 179975, "content": "“真的不是因为你，是我的问题”", "image": null, "praise_count": 25, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973026}, {"id": 180231, "content": "哎呀，又变穷光蛋了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 802718}, {"id": 180487, "content": "我一会就到，结果等了两个小时...", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 967776}, {"id": 181767, "content": "“行..吧...”", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 508977}, {"id": 179976, "content": "我没事", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973170}, {"id": 180488, "content": "占用大家一分钟，把这道题讲完", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974059}, {"id": 184328, "content": "马上=未知", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 983683}, {"id": 198153, "content": "真的，老好人。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1011736}, {"id": 179977, "content": "中国语言真是博大精深，一体两面", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 352556}, {"id": 180489, "content": "你真厉害", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 747016}, {"id": 192777, "content": "我听不懂你在说什么=别说了，不想再听", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1005686}, {"id": 179978, "content": "“不怪你”\n“不是你的错”", "image": null, "praise_count": 13, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 897571}, {"id": 180234, "content": "你的方案（论文）写的很好！但是还有点瑕疵需要改正。【你写的什么鬼东西！回去重写！】", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 931221}, {"id": 182026, "content": "时间有限，我只说三点。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 957825}, {"id": 185610, "content": "你肚子饿了吗(我肚子饿了，想吃饭了)", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 965807}, {"id": 179979, "content": "哦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 971989}, {"id": 180491, "content": "啦啦啦", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974367}, {"id": 179980, "content": "呵呵", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973178}, {"id": 180236, "content": "哦那算了", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973632}, {"id": 180492, "content": "是吗", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974367}, {"id": 180748, "content": "你不要怪我耿直", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 889841}, {"id": 181005, "content": "咱俩不合适", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 975709}, {"id": 179982, "content": "都是我的错", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 969964}, {"id": 183566, "content": "潜规则?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981805}, {"id": 180495, "content": "还可以", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974375}, {"id": 180240, "content": "你这次做的还不错", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 973642}, {"id": 180496, "content": "离职原因 总写“个人原因” ……  就是钱给少了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 974383}, {"id": 186128, "content": "晚安", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 989145}]}